      • loadCitibikeSample

        public org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.TemporalGraph loadCitibikeSample()
                                                                 throws Exception
        Loads citibike sample dataset as temporal graph. Uses start and end edge properties to set valid_from/tx_from and valid_to/tx_to values.
        Returns:
        temporal citibike sample graph

      • transformToTemporalGraph

        protected org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.TemporalGraph transformToTemporalGraph(org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.epgm.LogicalGraph logicalGraph)
        Given a logical graph, this method transforms it to a temporal graph. start and end values are extracted from the edges (= "trips") and used to set valid_from/tx_from and valid_to/tx_to values.
        Parameters:
        logicalGraph - the logical graph to transform
        Returns:
        logical graph transformed to temporal graph
